o freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Verch Robert Calamor was born in 1279, in Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Philip ap Adam \"Fychan of Wernddu. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1279–":"1279–Surnud","1279–1392":"1279–1392","1302–1400":"1302–1400","1369–Male":"1369–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1279–Female":"1279–Surnud","1369":"1369","1302":"1302","1279":"1279","1400":"1400","1392":"1392","Wernddu, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales":"Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1279–":"1279–Kuollut","1279–1392":"1279–1392","1302–1400":"1302–1400","1369–Male":"1369–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1279–Female":"1279–Kuollut","1369":"1369","1302":"1302","1279":"1279","1400":"1400","1392":"1392","Wernddu, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Monmouthshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales":"Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1279–":"1279–Décédée","1279–1392":"1279–1392","1302–1400":"1302–1400","1369–Male":"1369–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1279–Female":"1279–Décédée","1369":"1369","1302":"1302","1279":"1279","1400":"1400","1392":"1392","Wernddu, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Monmouthshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales":"Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Bedwellty, Monmouthshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Verch 